## Acceptance Criteria

1. All API operations generate audit events automatically
2. Correlation IDs propagate across all service calls
3. Sensitive data is redacted according to configuration
4. Export supports CSV and JSON formats with compression
5. Retention policies can be configured per-category
6. Search returns results within 2 seconds for 30-day queries
7. ClickHouse receives audit events within 5 seconds
8. Audit events are tamper-evident (cannot be modified after creation)
9. Export jobs handle datasets up to 1M records
10. UI provides intuitive search and filter interface
11. Compliance report generation for SOC 2 audits
12. Performance: < 5ms overhead per request for audit logging

## Testing Strategy

- Unit tests for redaction service
- Integration tests for correlation propagation
- Load tests for high-volume audit logging
- E2E tests for export functionality
- Compliance tests for required audit fields

