## Testing Requirements

Reference: `flywheel_gateway-d8b`.

### Unit Tests
- [ ] Redaction rules remove secrets deterministically and preserve non-sensitive context
- [ ] Export formats (JSON/NDJSON) are schema-valid and stable across versions
- [ ] Retention policies apply correctly without deleting required audit records

### Integration Tests
- [ ] Mutating operations create audit events with correlation IDs and can be queried via REST

### Failure Mode Tests
- [ ] Export under load does not block core operations; partial failures return resumable job state

### E2E Tests
- [ ] Covered by `flywheel_gateway-tz4` critical-path E2E suite; add a focused E2E spec if this feature introduces unique user workflows
